+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "status": 1,
            "data": {
                "id": 1,
                "car_id": 1,
                "created_on": "2019-02-18T12:34:22",
                "status": "Pending",
                "price": "1,500,000.00",
                "price_offered": "1,000,000.00"
    
            }
        }
        
